                    "created": 1524060593,
                    "url": "http://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/273813538",
                    "title": "中兴被美国制裁，会给国人什么样的启示？",
                    "question_type": "normal",
                    "is_following": false,
                    "type": "question",
                    "id": 273813538
